<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">Home</a> &nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp; <a href="medicare-basics.html">Plans</a> &nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp; Medicare Advantage</div>
    <h1>Medicare Advantage Plans in Utah</h1>
    <p class="lede">All-in-one Medicare plans that bundle hospital, medical, and usually drug coverage &mdash; often with extras like dental, vision, and hearing.</p>
  </div>
